quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,26,jin logon ne BHALAI ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya un ke liye BHALAI hai aur mazeed fazl un ke cheharon par roo siyahi aur zillat nah chaaye gi woh jannat ke mustahiq hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge
10,27,"aur jin logon ne buraiyan kamaain un ki buraii jaisi hai waisa hi woh badla payen ge, zillat un par musallat ho gi, koi Allah se un ko bachanay wala nah ho ga, un ke cheharon par aisi tareqi chhai hui ho gi jaisay raat ke siyah parday un par parre hue hon, woh dozakh ke mustahiq hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge"
10,28,"jis roz hum un sab ko aik sath ( apni adalat mein ) akhatta karen ge, phir un logon se jinhon ne shirk kya hai kahein ge ke tehrjao tum bhi aur tumahray banaye hue shareek bhi, phir hum un ke darmain se ajnabaiyat ka parda hata den ge aur un ke shareek kahin ge ke “ tum hamari ibadat to nahi karte thay"
10,29,"hamaray aur tumahray darmain Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai ke ( tum agar hamari ibadat karte bhi thay to ) hum tumhari is ibadat se bilkul be khabar thay """
10,30,"uss waqt har shakhs apne kiye ka maza chakh le ga, sab apne maalik haqeeqi ki taraf phair diye jayen ge aur woh saaray jhoot jo unhon ne ghurr rakhay thay gum ho jayen ge"
10,31,"inn se pucho, kon tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta hai? yeh samaat aur benaye ki quwaten kis ke ikhtiyar mein hain? kon be jaan mein se jandaar ko aur jandaar mein se be jaan ko nkalta hai? kon iss nazam aalam ki tadbeer kar raha hai? woh zaroor kahin ge ke Allah kaho, phir tum ( haqeeqat ke khilaaf chalne se ) parhaiz nahi karte ?"
10,32,tab to yahi Allah tumhara haqeeqi rab hai phir haq ke baad gumraahi ke siwa aur kya baqi reh gaya? aakhir yeh tum kidhar phira-ay ja rahay ho ?
10,33,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, dekho ) is terhan nafarmani ikhtiyar karne walon par tumahray rab ki baat Sadiq aa gayi ke woh maan kar nah den ge"
